Alice Lake https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alice_Lake 0 Alice Lake (September 12, 1895 – November 15, 1967) was an American film actress. She began her career during the silent film era and often appeared in comedy shorts opposite Roscoe Arbuckle. Alice_Lake ( September_12_,_1895 – November_15_,_1967 ) was an_American_film_actress .
